name: Aries
traits: Brave, Independent and Assertive. You are impulsive and hate to be restricted.

name: Taurus
traits: Sensual, have good taste, down to earth, pleasure seeking and stubborn.

name: Gemini
traits: Dynamic, with many talents. You like games, and are two-faced and mischievous.

name: Cancer
traits: Sensitive, friend-oriented, practical, and you hate to argue. You do forgive but you do not forget!

name: Leo
traits: Creative, popular, faithful, dominating, and you also have too much pride!

name: Virgo
traits: Successful, creative, and like to please. You are also clever, and can lead others on.

name: Libra
traits: Irresistible, adventurous, lavish. You are also indecisive, and have a complicated love life.

name: Scorpio
traits: Self reliant, powerful, and wise. You are also dominant and secretive.

name: Sagittarius
traits: Open-minded, achiever, and loving. You are also insensitive and cold.

name: Capricorn
traits: Hardworking, Straightforward, Loyal, Stubborn, and you are not content until at the top.

name: Aquarius
traits: Setting trends, innovative, and admired. You are also distant and eccentric.

name: Pisces
traits: Alluring, free, and sensual. You are also sensitive and cannot function alone.
